@node Main "Imito - Documentation"

                               'Imito' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Imito' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where the goal is to place tiles
so they match the coloured background pattern. There are two ways
to play the game:

-@{"Normal game" link play}:   You must 'rotate' the tiles by 90 degrees
                (clockwise) by clicking on them.

-@{"Slide-em game" link play}: A variation to the usual 'sliding-tiles' type of
                game, where the game tiles can move toward an
                empty space, *if* the tile to be moved has a
                'link' that points toward the empty space,
                otherwise, that tile will turn by 90 degrees...

  Complete each game board in the least amount of moves...

  Have fun!

